  "title": "Solutions Architect (Perm Role)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Solutions Architect (Data & Multimedia Platforms)</strong></h3><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>We’re looking for a Solution Architect to lead the design and delivery of data-driven platforms using tools like <strong>Denodo</strong>, <strong>Dataiku</strong>, and <strong>FFmpeg</strong>. You’ll work across teams to build secure, scalable solutions that support analytics, data virtualization, and media processing.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Design and implement solutions across data integration, analytics, and multimedia workflows</li><li>Lead architecture for platforms like Denodo, Dataiku, and FFmpeg</li><li>Translate business needs into scalable, secure technical solutions</li><li>Collaborate with engineers, architects, and stakeholders to drive delivery</li><li>Guide best practices, review designs, and ensure solution compliance</li><li>Stay updated on trends in data platforms, cloud, and media tech</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>6+ years in solution architecture or related roles</li><li>Experience with Denodo, Dataiku, or similar data/analytics platforms</li><li>Familiarity with FFmpeg or media processing tools</li><li>Strong knowledge of data systems, APIs, and cloud services (AWS, Azure, or GCP)</li><li>Excellent communication and problem-solving skills</li></ul><p><strong>Your recruiter for this job:</strong><br />WhatsApp <strong>Chally</strong> @ 6304 8675 for a quicker response<br />Connect with me on<br /> <strong>LinkedIn:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/cadeguino/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/cadeguino/</a><br /> <strong>Chally | chally@talentsis.com.sg</strong><br /> <strong>Talentsis Pte Ltd | EA No: 20C0312</strong></p>",
